{"tid":206210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"碩士生墮電騙失25萬","createTime":"2017-04-18T08:56:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T09:33:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8f9ed02015a62db10290b218c3ab3a2918bfc2ff","tid":206210,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T08:56:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170418/s00002/1492451138722\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170418%2Fs00002%2F1492451138722&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=3c038d3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170418%2Fs00002%2F1492451138722&h=51e1296f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170418/s00002/1492451138722</a><br />\n<br />\n碩士生墮電騙失25萬<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】再有市民誤墮電話騙案。一名新移民女碩士學生早前誤墮「內地官員」電話騙案，戶口被轉走約25萬元，至前晚發覺受騙後報警。<br />\n「內地檢察官」涉指金融罪行<br />\n女事主姓張，28歲，在港修讀碩士課程，據悉為新移民。消息稱，早前張接獲自稱「內地檢察官」男子電話，指她涉及金融罪行，要求她提供個人銀行戶口及密碼資料助查。張不虞有詐，向對方提供相關資料，其後發現戶口遭人分數次轉走共約22萬元人民幣（約24.8萬港元）。前晚11時許，張女在紅磡港鐵站報案。警方列作「以欺騙手段取得財產」案處理，交由九龍城警區刑事調查隊第7隊跟進。"},{"pid":"1c8a38573ef46050313e0acb320e06b0a9c1c7fa","tid":206210,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T09:05:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HPLG040.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHPLG040.jpg&h=7a2ddce8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c9b645789b2b62a1c13a1a8561ff2901289c2e6","tid":206210,"uid":8334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T09:06:01.000Z","msg":"蠢撚到, 個碩士學位係咪買返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b4ad671b183108c00d9c502af871c06e2feaa30","tid":206210,"uid":70727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T09:10:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蠢撚到, 個碩士學位